text: Sara Agrež (born 9 December 2000) is a Slovenian footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Slovenia women's national team. ==Career== Agrež has been capped for the Slovenia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian women's footballers Category:Slovenia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:1.
